# 🖥️ IT Service Desk – 3-Agent LangGraph System

## What you will build
A multi-agent AI pipeline that handles IT support tickets automatically:

```
User Ticket
    ↓
[Agent 1: Triage]     → classifies category + priority
    ↓
[Agent 2: Resolution] → attempts to solve the issue
    ↓  (if unsolvable)
[Agent 3: Escalation] → creates report for senior team
```

---

## Step 0 — Prerequisites (install these first)

| Tool | Why | Install link |
|------|-----|-------------|
| Python 3.10+ | Runs the code | https://python.org |
| VS Code | Write code comfortably | https://code.visualstudio.com |
| OpenAI API key | Powers the LLM | https://platform.openai.com |

---

## Step 1 — Set up your project folder

```bash
# Create folder
mkdir it_service_desk
cd it_service_desk

# Create virtual environment (keeps packages isolated)
python -m venv venv

# Activate it
# On Mac/Linux:
source venv/bin/activate
# On Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate
```

---

## Step 2 — Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## Step 3 — Set your API key

Create a file called `.env` in the project folder:

```
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-key-here
```

Then add this to the top of `agents.py` (already included):

```python
from dotenv import load_dotenv
load_dotenv()
```

